        <div class="pick-card">
          <span class="pick-type">Watch</span>
          <div class="pick-title">A World Cup Group Game — Any Group Game</div>
          <p class="pick-body">Pick a match this weekend involving a team you've never rooted for and give it 90 minutes of real attention. The 2026 expanded format means more underdog stories, stranger results, and more genuine surprise than any previous tournament. You'll find a team.</p>
          <span class="pick-where">Fox Sports · Telemundo · BBC iPlayer (UK)</span>
        </div>

        <div class="pick-card">
          <span class="pick-type">Listen</span>
          <div class="pick-title">Boards of Canada — <em>Inferno</em></div>
          <p class="pick-body">Best heard on headphones, in a dark room, with nothing competing for attention. Thirteen years is a long time, and they've been thinking. Whether or not it's their last record, it deserves a proper sit-down listen this weekend.</p>
          <span class="pick-where">Warp · Bandcamp · Spotify · Apple Music</span>
        </div>

        <div class="pick-card">
          <span class="pick-type">Read</span>
          <div class="pick-title">Paste Magazine: 'An Air of Finality Looms Over Boards of Canada's <em>Inferno</em>'</div>
